channel.title: Logo
channel.description:
Just a little something I made for my web design class using Fireworks. Comments please ;) I'm no hardcore graphics fanatic, just something I had to do for a grade. Took about 5 minutes, got an A ;)

item.title: Logo
item.dc:creator: @ninja_nub ninja nub
item.description:
@ninja_nub wrote:

Forgotten Hope:

It’s a hockey stop with some fading blending into the background…our teacher isn’t the best with graphics, it’s a web page design class and it’s mainly about php, html, etc. This is just a side unit. Like I said, I’m not some hardcore graphics fanatic…I made that the day I started fireworks and I thought it was cool.

I suggest you drop out of that class… NOW. If that’s how you would design something, you should go back 20 years and people might be impressed.
